{
  "stem": "7337.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 60.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So my grandfather called the two boys and said, now I can't afford to send more than one to university, when it's the oldest one's choice whether he wants to go to university or not.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my uncle said, yes, he wanted to become a lawyer.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he-- he went to university, and my father had to go into an apprenticeship.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And of the 11 sisters, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] 10 perished with their families-- that's husbands and children-- in the camps.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was never able to-- to trace them, because I didn't remember their married names.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I-- I-- I couldn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But not one came out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So those families all got killed in-- in the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "My grandfather was actually a boot maker, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and he made boots for Polish officers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] He had 24 workmen who all lived in.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you can imagine the family, therefore, consisted of 13 children, 24 workmen, and my grandfather and my grandmother.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And my grandmother cooked for that whole outfit.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, my father was born in '82.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So it must have been from '82 to '95.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] when he was 14, he left home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "My-- my grandfather had found him an apprenticeship, and he said, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] don't ever come home without a job, or I'll break every bone in your body.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And God bless you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was how-- how life went on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] My mother came from Alsace.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I think she was born in Metz, but she was educated in Budapest [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] before she came to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my parents met in-- in Berlin, and got married in 1913.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
